// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1988 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 2a4fd195-8899-5de2-85b9-18b05bd8aafc

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
